Instructions

The goal is to answer all ten questions correctly to win the game and pass the quiz.

First, to start the program press 1 on the keyboard. If you would like to quit at anytime during the quiz press 2. Finally to see the instructions again press 3.

Once you start the quiz, you will be presented with a math question and you will have to do the math to come up with the correct answer.

Once you have answered all the questions you will recieve a score at the end of the quiz. Keep in mind your score goal is a 10 and if you have less than that, you didn't pass and you can retake it.

If your score is a 10 then you are fine, but you can choose to retake it if you want.
